description:
src/lib.rs:162-174 — the format! is built inline with a nested ternary-style match, producing:

    format!(
        "HTTP {status} (check DOPPLER_TOKEN and project permissions){}",
        if detail.is_empty() {
            String::new()
        } else {
            format!(": {detail}")
        }
    )

This requires re-reading. Suggested rewrite (also fixes #5 by lifting into a helper):

    fn auth_aware_status(status: reqwest::StatusCode, detail: &str) -> SecretError {
        let suffix = if detail.is_empty() { String::new() } else { format!(": {detail}") };
        SecretError::Backend {
            backend: BACKEND,
            source: format!("HTTP {status} (check DOPPLER_TOKEN and project permissions){suffix}").into(),
        }
    }

then call it from get and put on 401/403.
